Questions I can now answer

  • The white house... what does it look like ?

    The white house is a big white building where Bill Clinton lives. It also happens to be the home of our president, Hillary.

    Return to list of questions.

  • How do you "Surf" the web ?

     Well, first you have to buy yourself a killer, web board. Then you have to put plenty of cyberwax on the surface so you don't slip. Then, all yu have to do is paddle out. If you're lucky, you can catch a Mosaic wave.

    Return to list of questions.

  • Is there really such thing as a free lunch ?

     Before the web, I thought the answer was no. Then I found what I was looking for. A Cybersandwich.

    Return to list of questions.

  • Do dinosaurs really exist ?

     I thought that dinosaurs went out after the late cretatious period. Then one day, I was fooling around on the web, and I made an important scientific discovery. I found dinosaurs at UC Berkley.

    Return to list of questions.

  • Where can I find great works of art on the web ?

     I found this... uh ..huh..huhu..huhuhhhhh..cool page. It's got like, huh..huh.. cool art. I even found a cool chick.*Blushes..* She's got a nice butt... huh..huh... After class, Beavis and I needed to let off some steam. So we decided to, like... prune some trees. Then we like, found this dog... and gave it a bath. That was really cool.
